Rhonda & Monica sharing our wonderful experience from yesterday. Everyone there was so welcoming & inviting from when we first stepped foot in the door. We loved that this was a family owned business built around love; it was truly evident in our conversations getting to know them while waiting on our food which didn't take long. And the food!
